<div class="dialog"
    role="dialog"
    aria-modal="true"
    aria-labelledby="game-3_label" 
    id="game-3">
    <div class="dialog__backdrop dialog-close"></div>
    <div class="dialog__content">
        
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:gap-8">
            <div>
                <header class="dialog__header">
                    <h2 id="game-3_label" class="dialog__title">Candy Math Land</h2>
                </header>
                <div class="dialog__info">
                    <div class="dialog__info-item">
                        <span class="dialog__info-label">Genre:</span>
                        <span class="dialog__info-value">Serius Game for learn math.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dialog__info-item">
                        <span class="dialog__info-label">Platforms:</span>
                        <span class="dialog__info-value">Android - iOS</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dialog__info-item">
                        <span class="dialog__info-label">Release Date:</span>
                        <span class="dialog__info-value">2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dialog__info-item">
                        <span class="dialog__info-label">Rating:</span>
                        <span class="dialog__info-value">5 - 8</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="dialog__body">
                    <p class="dialog__message">
                        The game revolves around creating a small, candy-themed world where the player (child) must face enemies (candies). To defeat these enemies (eat them), the player needs to empower their hero using magical math answers!
